relation: Darrow1 - #94 With his newly found hairstyle, Jeff discovers just how ruthless the picture man is to get his prize winning photos. Just how did he get that picture, anyways?

Darrow1 - #95 Thanks to the Mr. Saturn, Ness and friends have a chance to relax and wash off the filth of battle. Also, while Jeff cannot swim, the power of science allows him to still enjoy a peaceful dip. GO SCIENCE!
Darrow1 - #96 The Mr. Saturn show their thanks by offering up some delicious coffee. What Ness isn't aware of, however, is that Mr. Saturn have a whole other definition of what "coffee" is.
Darrow1 - #97 A wonderful journey begins as a disembodied voice runs Ness through the events that brought him to where he is now. Just who's been watching Ness all of this time?
Darrow1 - #98 The coffee raises some important questions for Ness to contemplate. I wish my coffee did that. Maybe it's just really shy.
